Small program package to make DB2 catalog evaluations
or to generate DDL for an object.
ZOS from  91 and LUW from 97 are supported.

You can always find the latest version at www.UBraeuer.de (DOWNLOAD)
If you have any questions, please email: ulrich_braeuerÂ§t-online.de




start the tool          ex_______ LUWDB2


#SSIDINF                control file for  SSID (Steplib, DBRMLIB,...)
                        This file should be adapted for the individual
                        subsystems

Nachfolgendes bitte nicht ANDERN |||||||

#STEULB5                Control file for  DB2 LUW V11.5
#STEULB1                Control file for  DB2 LUW V11.1
#STEULA5                Control file for  DB2 LUW V10.5
#STEULA1                Control file for  DB2 LUW V10.1
#STEUL97                Control file for  DB2 LUW V9.7
#STEUZB1                Control file for  DB2 ZOS V11
#STEUZA1                Control file for  DB2 ZOS V10
#STEUZ91                Control file for  DB2 ZOS V9
#STEUZ81                Control file for  DB2 ZOS V8

LUWB5*                  REXX'e for DB2 LUW V11.5
LUWB1*                  REXX'e for DB2 LUW V11.1
LUWA5*                  REXX'e for DB2 LUW V10.5
LUWA1*                  REXX'e for DB2 LUW V10.1
LUW97*                  REXX'e for DB2 LUW V 9.7
ZOSC1*                  REXX'e for DB2 ZOS V12
ZOSB1*                  REXX'e for DB2 ZOS V11
ZOSA1*                  REXX'e for DB2 ZOS V10
ZOS91*                  REXX'e for DB2 ZOS V 9
ZOS81*                  REXX'e for DB2 ZOS V 8
RX*                     REXX'e for other (BATCH)

current number  :

AC1                     generate DDL with DB2LK_GENERATE_DDL (LUW)
AC2                     generate DDL
AC3                     generate list for overview panel
200                     selection list overview
210                     Manage the object list
900                     Selection for branches
905                     Write Panel and Skeleton
906                     show Dynamic PANEL
910                     create select/delete, ... statements
911                     Execute Statement
915                     generate  Utilety Delete Grant
920                     create DDL Selection program calls AC2
925                     Alter Object (DB, TS, TB, .... )
930                     Explain and create Virtual Indexes too
935                     create Performance SQL's
940                     generate DSN1COPY
